{"id":15777,"date":"2022-09-29T16:36:38","date_gmt":"2022-09-29T20:36:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.rstp.ca\/?page_id=15777"},"modified":"2022-12-09T09:47:01","modified_gmt":"2022-12-09T14:47:01","slug":"afghanistan-public-policy-sessions","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.rstp.ca\/en\/training\/afghanistan-public-policy-sessions\/","title":{"rendered":"Special Program for Sponsoring Afghan Refugees"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>Special Program for Groups of Five and Community Sponsors to Sponsor Afghan Refugees without Proof of Refugee Status (RSD document)<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>IRCC announced a temporary public policy that enables Groups of Five and Community Sponsors to sponsor Afghan refugees who do not have a refugee status document issued by the United Nations Refugee Agency (UNHCR), or a foreign state, which formally recognizes the applicant as a refugee in early October, 2022. For information about the program go to this link: <a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fcorporate%2Fmandate%2Fpolicies-operational-instructions-agreements%2Fpublic-policies%2Fafghan-refugee-sponsorship-group-five-community-sponsor.html&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C69d6546f5e6e42e5b32c08daa5630632%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638004141978149264%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=tlPPHCQjsSlk5KBtK7jRpiwbHoodFVARSVH71Im81gk%3D&amp;reserved=0\">Temporary public policy to facilitate the sponsorship of Afghan refugees by groups of five and community sponsors \u2013 Canada.ca<\/a><\/p>\n<p>The special program to sponsor Afghan refugees without refugee status from the UNHCR or a foreign state is no longer accepting applications.\u00a0 The IRCC program has received the maximum number of applications and is full.<\/p>\n<p><strong>If you have already applied to the special program<\/strong>, IRCC will review and process the application. Information about the application process can be found in these guides:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Frefugees%2Fhelp-outside-canada%2Fprivate-sponsorship-program%2Fgroups-five%2Fafter-you-apply.html&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C209179cfa8174afbabbc08dad8a34eca%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638060493166406273%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=IbIsVbl0BUvX1DRR9imPFxv1I5auerasjbOIcYo94EQ%3D&amp;reserved=0\">Group of five<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Frefugees%2Fhelp-outside-canada%2Fprivate-sponsorship-program%2Fcommunity-sponsors%2Fafter-you-apply.html&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C209179cfa8174afbabbc08dad8a34eca%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638060493166406273%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=0ATBn%2FliFfwndpeyQbmIq9IfD2SWT7gnXVoyUqGJViY%3D&amp;reserved=0\">Community Sponsor<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>If there are any changes to your application<\/strong> &#8211; updated address, new telephone number or if the refugee moves &#8211; please inform IRCC as soon as possible. Information about how to contact IRCC is provided in the guides linked above.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Other sponsorship options for Afghan refugees:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>If an applicant has been recognized as a refugee by UNHCR or a foreign state<\/strong>, a sponsorship application can be submitted by a Group of Five or Community Sponsors. Please visit the RSTP website &#8211;\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rstp.ca%2F&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C209179cfa8174afbabbc08dad8a34eca%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638060493166406273%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=NGT8hPDW40yK0aqFzUIvFEWSUCmqBM4Q40ktrcYtt4Y%3D&amp;reserved=0\">www.rstp.ca<\/a>\u00a0&#8211; for more information and training sessions for these types of applications.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>If an applicant has not been recognized as a refugee<\/strong>, an application needs to be submitted by a Sponsorship Agreement Holder. Here is information about working with a Sponsorship Agreement Holder here:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Frefugees%2Fhelp-outside-canada%2Fprivate-sponsorship-program%2Fagreement-holders.html&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C209179cfa8174afbabbc08dad8a34eca%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638060493166406273%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=UnMlFDpMYn0jiXp1rrg4JYslYl%2B%2BsWzBzcAFt8YcOcA%3D&amp;reserved=0\">https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/en\/immigration-refugees-citizenship\/services\/refugees\/help-outside-canada\/private-sponsorship-program\/agreement-holders.html<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>If you have any additional questions or require specific information, please contact an RSTP trainer in your area. You can find a list of trainers here:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rstp.ca%2Fen%2Fcontact-us%2F&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C209179cfa8174afbabbc08dad8a34eca%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638060493166406273%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=gEdtbPdpdFvpTfxC%2FKpQ%2B5me7ylGzuFYeur7yQ3vOzc%3D&amp;reserved=0\"><strong>https:\/\/www.rstp.ca\/en\/contact-us\/<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p>For more details, please visit:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Frefugees%2Fafghanistan%2Fspecial-measures%2Fsponsor-without-rsd.html&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C69d6546f5e6e42e5b32c08daa5630632%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638004141978149264%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=9k%2BiAwyaFf%2Bd8MTh7DqRYwt4Kqid8jRQadH2%2FC5mYfM%3D&amp;reserved=0\">Updates on the Special program to sponsor Afghan refugees without refugee status from the UNHCR or a foreign state \u2013 Canada.ca<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/can01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fcorporate%2Fmandate%2Fpolicies-operational-instructions-agreements%2Fpublic-policies%2Fafghan-refugee-sponsorship-group-five-community-sponsor.html&amp;data=05%7C01%7C%7C69d6546f5e6e42e5b32c08daa5630632%7Ca5827fca282b40a69875772ff7768431%7C0%7C0%7C638004141978149264%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=tlPPHCQjsSlk5KBtK7jRpiwbHoodFVARSVH71Im81gk%3D&amp;reserved=0\">Temporary public policy to facilitate the sponsorship of Afghan refugees by groups of five and community sponsors \u2013 Canada.ca<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.rstp.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/FAQs-on-Afgan-Public-Policy-RSTPOct16revised.pdf\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Special Program for Groups of Five and Community Sponsors to Sponsor Afghan Refugees without Proof of Refugee Status (RSD document) IRCC announced a temporary public policy that enables Groups of [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":15,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status